# Email Configuration for Feedback System

# Option 1: For Gmail
EMAIL_SERVICE=gmail
EMAIL_USER=your-gmail-address@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password-from-google
EMAIL_RECIPIENT=where-to-receive-feedback@example.com

# Option 2: For other SMTP providers (uncomment and use these instead)
# EMAIL_HOST=smtp.example.com
# EMAIL_PORT=587
# EMAIL_SECURE=false
# EMAIL_USER=your-email@example.com
# EMAIL_PASS=your-password
# EMAIL_RECIPIENT=where-to-receive-feedback@example.com

# How to get a Gmail App Password:
# 1. Enable 2-Step Verification on your Google Account
# 2. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Select "Mail" and your device
# 4. Google will generate a 16-character password for you to use 